{
  "stem": "14060.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "Not in Czech land-- the Czechs are very-- I must add them to the list of, [LAUGHS] of decent people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "The, the-- Tiso, who was the-- was a priest, who was the head of the Slovakian puppet German regime-- Today, we have got Slovakia independent for the second time in its history, the same as Croatia; they were only independent states during Hitler time-- was the only person-- and he was a Catholic priest, if you please-- who paid the German treasury money for each Jew they deported.",
      "word_count": 68
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "Not even the Austrians did that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "Probably they are too stingy for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "He literally paid the German treasury for every Jew they deported.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What sort of priest is that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What sort of person is that who pays to kill other people but under any state?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As it happens, he was hanged after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And today, they are rehabilitating him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People don't change.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Take it from me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not suffering from any emotional disturbance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not having any particular animosity more than necessary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I say to you that to reeducate people takes a hell of a long time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people are very, very hard to change.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would say, probably, coming strangely from me, the most reeducation post-war I think happened in Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Germans are probably much larger thinking than some of these small European countries.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They are too small-minded to change.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they are too nationalistic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Germans are also nationalistic, but maybe in a larger context.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They want to rule the whole of Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They're not interested just to control the minorities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And really, things haven't changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
